Author: reallyshameful
Text: Reality   I refuse to weigh in medical settings  Too many variables  I don't want calibration paranoia about my home scale  I ask for a blind weigh if I can't avoid it  Keep my weight to yourself, sisbro

Text: gOD something similar happened to me a while back. They switched the last two digits on accident so instead of it being 29 it was 92 and I about cried
